{"tid":2334790,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【武漢肺炎】政府午夜起禁英國客機抵港　曾稱基本法保障出入自由不能封關","createTime":"2020-12-21T11:17:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-21T14:48:39.000Z","uid":51271,"like":5,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"98bb58ca7f97ccaffd0a05245550de8bc2a3e42d","tid":2334790,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T11:17:21.000Z","msg":"同是港人唔同命？<br />\n<br />\n【武漢肺炎】政府午夜起禁英國客機抵港 曾稱基本法保障出入自由不能封關<br />\n武漢肺炎疫情爆發以來，市民多次提出希望政府封關，行政長官林鄭月娥和特區政府則一直強調，基本法保障出入境自由，故不能「封關」將從外地回港的香港居民拒諸門外。<br />\n但政府今日宣布，午夜起停止所有英國來港航班，兩星期內曾到英國的人，亦不能登上來港航班，包括香港居民，食衛局長陳肇始今日在記者會，多次被問到兩者是否有矛盾，她表示已經和律政司研究，認為做法穩妥。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/society/%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E5%8D%88%E5%A4%9C%E8%B5%B7%E7%A6%81%E8%8B%B1%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%A2%E6%A9%9F%E6%8A%B5%E6%B8%AF-%E9%99%90%E8%81%9A%E4%BB%A4-%E6%99%9A%E5%B8%82%E7%A6%81%E5%A0%82%E9%A3%9F%E7%AD%89%E6%A9%AB%E8%B7%A8%E8%81%96%E8%AA%95%E6%96%B0%E5%B9%B4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E-%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25BA%259C%25E5%258D%2588%25E5%25A4%259C%25E8%25B5%25B7%25E7%25A6%2581%25E8%258B%25B1%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25AE%25A2%25E6%25A9%259F%25E6%258A%25B5%25E6%25B8%25AF-%25E9%2599%2590%25E8%2581%259A%25E4%25BB%25A4-%25E6%2599%259A%25E5%25B8%2582%25E7%25A6%2581%25E5%25A0%2582%25E9%25A3%259F%25E7%25AD%2589%25E6%25A9%25AB%25E8%25B7%25A8%25E8%2581%2596%25E8%25AA%2595%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%25B9%25B4%2F&d=Yr0hxYoWOJ9ZaoTMuy4WzCEyVFbloTKGHdwbQdNTMZo%3D&h=ca7bb9ec\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E-%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25BA%259C%25E5%258D%2588%25E5%25A4%259C%25E8%25B5%25B7%25E7%25A6%2581%25E8%258B%25B1%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25AE%25A2%25E6%25A9%259F%25E6%258A%25B5%25E6%25B8%25AF-%25E9%2599%2590%25E8%2581%259A%25E4%25BB%25A4-%25E6%2599